                         <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/ask-the-expert-andre-cazelais\/\">\n                                        Ask the Expert: Andr\u00e9 Cazelais                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    For over 30 years, Andr\u00e9 Cazelais has been at the forefront of the&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    January 19, 2024                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n            <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-tree-green-color has-text-color\" id=\"priorite-climatique\"><strong>Priorit\u00e9 climatique.<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Pour ralentir le r\u00e9chauffement plan\u00e9taire et att\u00e9nuer les pires impacts du changement climatique, il faut accro\u00eetre l\u2019efficacit\u00e9 \u00e9nerg\u00e9tique et diminuer les \u00e9missions de carbone. Les b\u00e2timents \u00e0 carbone z\u00e9ro offrent une solution tant pour les nouveaux b\u00e2timents que pour les b\u00e2timents existants et ils peuvent stimuler la croissance \u00e9conomique et la cr\u00e9ation de nouveaux emplois hautement qualifi\u00e9s.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading has-h-8-font-size\" id=\"argumentation-a-l-appui\"><strong><strong>Argumentation \u00e0 l\u2019appui<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Le rapport du CBDCA sur les <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/arguments-en-faveur-des-batiments-a-carbone-zero\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Arguments en faveur des b\u00e2timents \u00e0 carbone z\u00e9ro<\/a> prouve que les b\u00e2timents \u00e0 carbone z\u00e9ro sont techniquement r\u00e9alisables et financi\u00e8rement viables. L\u2019investissement dans des b\u00e2timents \u00e0 carbone z\u00e9ro offre une protection contre la hausse du co\u00fbt du carbone tout en apportant des avantages qui vont au-del\u00e0 de la r\u00e9duction du carbone.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/portal.cagbc.org\/cagbcdocs\/advocacy\/CBDCa_Arguments_en_faveur_du_b%C3%A2timent_%C3%A0_carbone_z%C3%A9ro_%282019%29_FR.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Argumentation \u00e0 l\u2019appui&nbsp;: <\/span>Lire le r\u00e9sum\u00e9<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading has-h-8-font-size\"><strong><strong>D\u00e9carbonation des grands b\u00e2timents du Canada<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Pour que le Canada atteigne ses cibles en mati\u00e8re d\u2019\u00e9missions de carbone, il faut que les b\u00e2timents existants soient modernis\u00e9s ou r\u00e9nov\u00e9s. L\u2019\u00e9tude du CBDCA sur la <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/decarbonation-des-grands-batiments-du-canada\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">D\u00e9carbonation des grands b\u00e2timents du Canada<\/a> examine les propri\u00e9taires d&#8217;immeubles peuvent utiliser des r\u00e9novations profondes pour acc\u00e9l\u00e9rer la d\u00e9carbonation des b\u00e2timents.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/portal.cagbc.org\/cagbcdocs\/advocacy\/2021_CaGBC_Decarbonization-Retrofit-Costing-Study_2DEC21_FR.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">D\u00e9carbonation des grands b\u00e2timents du Canada&nbsp;: <\/span>Lire le r\u00e9sum\u00e9<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n    <div class=\"is-style-section-headline \">\n        <h2 class=\"has-h-4-font-size spacing-bottom-0\" id=\"h-news-articles-65b60e39b206f\">RECHERCHES LES PLUS R\u00c9CENTES<\/h2>\n        <div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n            <div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main is-style-main--small\">\n                <a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color\" aria-describedby=\"h-news-articles-65b60e39b206f\" href=\"                    \">LIRE PLUS                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n                <div class=\"wp-custom-grid\">\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/dans-quels-cas-des-batiments-multiples-peuvent-ils-viser-ensemble-la-certification-leed\/\">\n                                        Dans quels cas des b\u00e2timents multiples peuvent-ils viser ensemble la certification LEED?                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Lorsqu\u2019un projet comprend plus d\u2019un b\u00e2timent situ\u00e9s sur un m\u00eame site et g\u00e9r\u00e9s&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    January 26, 2024                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/when-can-multiple-buildings-pursue-leed-certification-together\/\">\n                                        When can multiple buildings pursue LEED certification together?                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    When a project consists of more than one building sharing a common site&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    January 26, 2024                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/demandez-a-lexpert-andre-cazelais\/\">\n                                        Demandez \u00e0 l&#8217;expert : Andr\u00e9 Cazelais                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Depuis plus de 30 ans, Andr\u00e9 Cazelais est \u00e0 l\u2019avant-plan des efforts de&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    January 19, 2024                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/ask-the-expert-andre-cazelais\/\">\n                                        Ask the Expert: Andr\u00e9 Cazelais                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    For over 30 years, Andr\u00e9 Cazelais has been at the forefront of the&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    January 19, 2024                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n            <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-tree-green-color has-text-color\" id=\"batiment-a-carbone-zero-et-emplois\"><strong>B\u00e2timent \u00e0 carbone z\u00e9ro et emplois<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Dans la course \u00e0 la r\u00e9duction des \u00e9missions de carbone et \u00e0 l\u2019atteinte des cibles climatiques du Canada, les b\u00e2timents et les r\u00e9novations \u00e0 carbone z\u00e9ro constituent une strat\u00e9gie importante. D\u2019ailleurs, le gouvernement f\u00e9d\u00e9ral exige d\u00e9j\u00e0 que tous les b\u00e2timents qui lui appartiennent ou qu\u2019il loue visent le carbone z\u00e9ro. Plus les propri\u00e9taires de b\u00e2timents seront nombreux \u00e0 lui embo\u00eeter le pas, plus la demande pour des emplois dans le domaine du b\u00e2timent durable augmentera.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Le rapport du CBDCA intitul\u00e9 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/le-batiment-durable-comme-element-moteur-au-canada\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Le b\u00e2timent durable comme \u00e9l\u00e9ment moteur au Canada<\/a>&nbsp;estime que le nombre d\u2019emplois directs en b\u00e2timent durable pourrait s\u2019\u00e9tablir \u00e0 1,5 million d\u2019ici 2030 si le gouvernement s\u2019engage dans une reprise verte pour contrer les impacts \u00e9conomiques de la pand\u00e9mie de COVID-19. Les investissements dans le perfectionnement de la main-d\u2019\u0153uvre seront toutefois n\u00e9cessaires pour r\u00e9pondre aux exigences techniques des b\u00e2timents \u00e0 carbone z\u00e9ro.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/\">LIRE LE RAPPORT<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0px\">\n    <div class=\"is-style-section-headline \">\n        <h2 class=\"has-h-4-font-size spacing-bottom-0\" id=\"h-news-articles-65b60e39b69fa\">DERNI\u00c8RES NOUVELLES<\/h2>\n        <div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n            <div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main is-style-main--small\">\n                <a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color\" aria-describedby=\"h-news-articles-65b60e39b69fa\" href=\"                    \">LIRE PLUS                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n                <div class=\"wp-custom-grid\">\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/dans-quels-cas-des-batiments-multiples-peuvent-ils-viser-ensemble-la-certification-leed\/\">\n                                        Dans quels cas des b\u00e2timents multiples peuvent-ils viser ensemble la certification LEED?                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Lorsqu\u2019un projet comprend plus d\u2019un b\u00e2timent situ\u00e9s sur un m\u00eame site et g\u00e9r\u00e9s&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                       